<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ro">
  <head>
    <%- include('../fragmente/head', { title: title }) %>
  </head>
  <body>
    <%- include('../fragmente/header') %>

    <main>
      <section id="welcome">
        <h2><%= heading %></h2>
        <p>Pagina este randata cu EJS, iar head, header si footer sunt incluse din fragmente reutilizabile.</p>
      </section>

      <section id="video-vtt">
        <h2>Review Video: Nike Ja 3</h2>
        <p>Clipul are subtitrari in romana si engleza. Subtitrarea in romana este implicita.</p>

        <video
          class="video-vtt-player"
          controls
          preload="auto"
          poster="/src/images/jersey.jpg"
        >
          <source src="/src/videos/ja3-review.mp4" type="video/mp4" />
          <source src="/src/videos/ja3-review.wmv" type="video/x-ms-wmv" />

          <track
            src="/src/videos/subtritari/ja3-review-ro.vtt"
            kind="subtitles"
            srclang="ro"
            label="Romana"
            default
          />
          <track
            src="/src/videos/subtritari/ja3-review-en.vtt"
            kind="subtitles"
            srclang="en"
            label="English"
          />

          Browserul tau nu suporta redarea video HTML5.
        </video>
      </section>

      <%- include('../fragmente/date-utilizator') %>
    </main>

    <%- include('../fragmente/footer') %>
  </body>
</html>
